ttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67QwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=67bdba8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/vK4Dfno.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvK4Dfno.png&h=f4f33a64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RCDXv4t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRCDXv4t.jpg&h=c2140d08&s={SIZE}\" /> </div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4.追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>七區集會</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n  日期：8月5日<br />\n  時間：下午一時開始<br />\n各區地點：金鐘添馬公園、旺角麥花臣球場、沙田百步梯、大埔廣福球場、荃灣沙咀道球場、黃大仙廣場、屯門公園<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttLCv36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttLCv36.jpg&h=09ba4839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NKejKpu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNKejKpu.jpg&h=f51b4d73&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"1058d6c1ccd89e021dfc26e4aad3807d7dd1c4e3","tid":1380982,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:57:48.000Z","msg":"邊個口號最鼓勵到士氣咪嗌邊個<br />\n「光復香港 時代革命」嘅氣勢大家有眼見"},{"pid":"00b02b5d964268790c2703fb785afe14a012db7c","tid":1380982,"uid":286990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:03:23.000Z","msg":"兩個月以黎<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong